SummaryContractDeliverableForm is a SummaryForm
    title is "ContractDeliverableInformation"
    Layout
        two column
            Contract
            Contract.Name
        single column
            Name
            Description
            DueDate
            DeliveredDate
            Quantity
            Rate
            Amount
            PersonResponsible
        paragraph
            paragraph
                NumberOfDaysToFirstAlert
                    label is "FirstAlert_(Yellow)Is"
                text of "DaysBeforeDueDate."
            paragraph
                NumberOfDaysToSecondAlert
                    label is "SecondAlert_(Red)Is"
                text of "DaysBeforeDueDate."
        visible when (CommentsExist)
            list is ContractDeliverableComment set.ContractDeliverableCommentsPrint
